                    <span>People spend their entire lifetimes working to amass wealth, but forget about protecting it. I bump into people every day who still think a will is enough---ENT! I also recommend Financial Self Defense and More Wealth  without Risk by Givens. Suze's book is newer, but Givens offers techniques  that work well with the information in this book.</span>
                  
              
